{"componentChunkName":"component---src-page-post-tsx","path":"/success-through-humanness","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Markus Tacker","tagLine":"Software Crafter","description":"Software Crafter building üå©Ô∏è cloud-based cellular IoT solutions at Nordic Semiconductor.‚Äã\n\t\tMentor. Speaker. ‚ÄãConference & Community builder. Camper. üèïÔ∏è üöê","gitHubUrl":"https://github.com/coderbyheart/coderbyheart.com.git","siteUrl":"https://coderbyheart.com","twitter":"@coderbyheart","defaultCard":"https://images.ctfassets.net/bncv3c2gt878/3Jk4P6nFPNzaz1gsguktk8/350b7e4ddb2c7d86416243d9902920e2/social-card-default-2020.png"}}},"pageContext":{"page":{"id":"910f70fe-4cd4-509b-95fd-0d89af274e2a","name":"success-through-humanness","relativeDirectory":"post","relativePath":"post/success-through-humanness.md","remark":{"htmlAst":{"children":[{"children":[{"properties":{"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/bncv3c2gt878/3uWbQ5sUFoYp7hGxJQ4ZAj/b390dd35af6b8042c9b25e541f6e14d3/success-through-humanness.jpg?w=1947&h=1296","alt":"Womit ich nie gerechnet habe"},"children":[],"tagName":"img","type":"element"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Womit ich nie gerechnet habe"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://amzn.to/1YyyHvl","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" is the (German) autobiography by the founder\nof "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"dm"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":", today the largest pharmacy retailer in Europe. Within 35 years, Werner\nbuild an organization of 30,000 employees and 2,000 stores in 2008 based on\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"anthroposophical principles developed by Rudolf Steiner"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anthroposophy","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":": putting the human\nfirst, within the organization but also in relation to the customer."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The book is unique because it offers a fascinating insight into a journey of a\nfounder who learned that you can run a profitable, agile and antifragile\nbusiness while ignoring industries best practices and putting the individual\nfirst."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"In this book Werner describes his way from a young pharmacist when he started\nseeing opportunities where others wouldn't to the CEO of a successful pharmacy\nretailer and describes multiple occasions where the organization needed to be\ncompletely restructured. The reasons were never due to a crisis but due to\nWerner's strive to build a company that "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"serves"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" its employees, customers and\nthe society. By questioning the status quo and pushing for his idealistic views,\noften answered with strong hesitation by colleagues and friends, he enabled "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"dm"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\nto be truly agile: change was achieved by engaging everyone in the organization,\nwhich often took years. But because everyone "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"owned"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" the change it never failed\nto stick. His effort to improve the human factor in the organization proved to\nbe a win-win for everyone: the company never made losses, it holds the highest\nrating in independent consumer satisfaction rankings, is a highly favored\nemployer and the market leader in Europe."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Werner's legacy is proof that it is possible to build a successful business in a\nhighly competitive market without sacrificing purpose and generosity. A business\nthat includes the human needs and messiness into the business model will be at\nleast as successful as "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"classical"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" meat-grinders. Examples like the Schlecker\nbankruptcy showed that this approach pays off."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"I recommend this book to everyone who is facing problems like high turnover\nrates, inefficiency due to bureaucracy and incompetence or is, like me,\ninterested in alternative operating-systems for organizations."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"}],"type":"root","data":{"quirksMode":false}},"frontmatter":{"title":"Success through humanness: The autobiography by dm founder G√∂tz W. Werner","subtitle":"Book review","noheadline":null,"date":"2016-06-18T08:00:00.000Z","abstract":"Book review of Womit ich nie gerechnet habe by G√∂tz W. Werner.   I recommend this book to everyone who is facing problems like high turnover rates, inefficiency due to bureaucracy and incompetence or is, like me, interested in alternative operating-systems for organizations.\n","lang":null},"headings":[]}},"Footer":{"id":"cfe5b9e2-511c-5615-992a-dab82e1f8ed7","name":"Footer","relativeDirectory":"","relativePath":"Footer.md","remark":{"htmlAst":{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Software Crafte